      *
       CLEAR-SCREEN SECTION.
       CLEAR-000.
           CALL "XE4".
           MOVE SPACES TO WS-MESSAGE
           MOVE 0300 TO POS.
       CLEAR-015.
           DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE AT POS.
           IF POS < 3100
              ADD 100 TO POS
              GO TO CLEAR-015.
       CLEAR-999.
           EXIT.
